OL,5, A hosepipe and sprinkler ban has been  
OL,6, imposed on people in Kent and Sussex.  
OL,8,FSouth East Water said it had no choice 
OL,9,Fafter demand for drinking water had    
OL,10,Freached "record levels" in June,       
OL,11,Fsimilar to last year's drought.        
OL,13,FUp to 4,000 customers are without water
OL,14,For have been experiencing low pressure 
OL,15,Fsince Monday due to supply issues.     
OL,17,FThe water company had urged people to  
OL,18,Fonly use water for essential purposes, 
OL,19,Fbut has now issued an immediate ban on 
OL,20,Fhosepipes and sprinklers.              
